Interface CommandStrategy

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ActivateClientCommandStrategy, ApplyLoanCommandStrategy, ApplySavingsCommandStrategy, ApproveLoanCommandStrategy, CollectChargesCommandStrategy, CreateChargeCommandStrategy, CreateClientCommandStrategy, DisburseLoanCommandStrategy, UnknownCommandStrategy, UpdateClientCommandStrategy

    public interface CommandStrategy
    An interface for various Command Strategies. It contains a single function which returns appropriate response from a particular command strategy.

    Rishabh Shukla
